Consume			KEY:Maurezhi ~ Consume			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MaurezhiRaceTrait.SpecialQuality		VISIBLE:YES		DESC:When a maurezhi slays a sentient living creature and consumes the body, it gains power. It must begin eating the corpse within 10 minutes of its death and requires 30 minutes to complete consumption. If the process is interrupted no benefits are gained. Consumed creatures are difficult to restore to life (see text).The maurezhi gains access to the memories, language, and form of the eaten creature.
Pounce			KEY:Maurezhi ~ Pounce			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MaurezhiRaceTrait.SpecialQuality		VISIBLE:YES		DESC:If a maurezhi charges, it can make a full attack even though it has moved.
Paralysis		KEY:Maurezhi ~ Paralysis		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MaurezhiRaceTrait.SpecialQuality		VISIBLE:YES		DESC:Any creature hit by a maurezhi's claw or bite attack must succeed on a Fortitude save (DC %1, DC 10 + 1/2 HD + CON) or be paralyzed for 1d6+4 minutes.|(10 + TL + CON)
Assume Shape		KEY:Maurezhi ~ Assume Shape		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MaurezhiRaceTrait.SpecialQuality		VISIBLE:YES		DESC:A maurezhi can take on the appearance of any humanoid creature whose corpse it has eaten and can hold the form indefinitely.
